Title: Maya's Cold Pressed Flaxseed Oil
Description: Cold pressed Flexseed oil is used to cure Arthritis, soriasis, Eczema, Acne and other illnesses and conditions.Among all 127 World's Healthiest Foods, flaxseeds comes out number one as a source of omega-3s.The second unique feature of flaxseed is its lignans. "Mucilage" refers to water-soluble, gel-forming fiber that can provide special support to the intestinal tract.

Title: Mayasnaturals Cold Pressed Sesame Oil
Description: Mayasnaturals Sesame Oil Is Extracted Under Low-Temperature Conditions Using An Expeller Press In A Process Called Cold Pressing. So In A Way The Product You Get Is 100% Pure , Natural & Unfiltered . It Is A Rich Source Of Vitamin C, E & K. Sesame Oil Is Reputed To Penetrate The Skin Easily And Is Used In India For Oil Massage. It Is An Excellent Cure For Sensitive, Pigmented Skins.

Description: This fresh, gentle formula works on building and fattening the intercellular structure of the hair fibre with extracts of fennel and Visnaga vera. Increasing microcirculation in the scalp causes the microcapillaries of the skin to relax and open, boosting oxygen and nutrient delivery to the roots of the hair. This complex is further enhanced by the addition of betaine to strengthen hair fibre, and protein stabilised superoxide dismutase to protect hair colour, both natural and artificial, from solar damage.+ Vitamin A (Retinyl Palmitate) Included in high levels to normalise scalp function and oil production—this is especially beneficial for fine hair, which has a tendency to go limp with excess sebum. Vitamin A is also excellent in providing suppleness and sheen in hair.+ Baobab Extract (Hydrolysed Adansonia Digitata Extract) Plumps and bulks up each hair fibre with a light film to make hair feel fuller, thicker and more substantial.+ Vitamin B5 (D-Panthenol) Prevents hair damage through moisturisation and thickening to impart a high lustre and sheen. It has a small molecule so it can penetrate the hair cuticle easily, strengthening the internal structure by up to 20%.Multi Functional Tip+ Once lathered, leave Sans [ceuticals] Volumising Hair Wash in for a few minutes, allowing the actives to treat the hair and scalp, then rinse. For a more thorough cleanse, repeat.

Title: Majik 100% Human Hair Building Fiber 10 Soft Hair Volumizer Powder
Description: Hair loss is a very common problem that number of people suffer from. There are number of products available in the market to prevent this problem. If you are suffering from a drastic hair fall and partial baldness, you could opt for Hair Building Fiber by Majik. Majik is a Swiss based brand which is recognized as one of the most reputed hair-care brands all over the world. From the Manufacturer What It Is Majik Hair Building Fibers, made of 100% Human hair, blend undetectably with existing hair strands to instantly create the appearance of naturally thick and full hair. What It Does Instantly fills in thinning areas Conceals hair loss Makes fine hair look completely thick and full Great as a root touch-up between colorings What Else You Need To Know Majik Hair Fibers resist wind, rain, and perspiration for long lasting results in all conditions. Available in nine shades that can be mixed to match Indian hair color, Hair Fibers work for all hair types and textures. Also great for part lines, covering extension tracks and touching up roots between hair color appointments. Easily washes out with shampoo. How to Apply Dry and style hair as usual. Shake Hair Fibers into thinning areas. If applying Hair Fibers near the hairline, use Majik Hairline Optimizer to achieve a natural looking front hairline. Gently pat hair to disperse Hair Fibers. If desired, lightly comb, brush, or style your hair after applying Hair Fibers. For best results, use Majik Hair Fiber Spray to finish for longer-lasting results.
